Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭一天天临近了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们天天都是准备 准备 再准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 没看到矢野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 矢野 应该在这附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去给你找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能做到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿手的本领是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时何地 都能找到矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:06.03,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:11.93,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:17.90,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:23.80,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:30.93,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:35.93,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:38.89,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:50.43,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:55.41,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:02.60,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:07.43,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.45,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:06.03,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:11.93,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:17.90,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:23.80,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:30.93,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:35.93,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:42.19,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:50.43,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:55.41,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:02.60,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:07.43,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.45,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词背熟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不知怎么感觉他好像很冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我多心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从一起去吃肉包子那天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 怎么说呢 很难呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 暖和和的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和和的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 像肉包子啊 烤山芋之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒冷时可以取暖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让心觉得温暖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以是喜欢的书啦 CD啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的…人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去吃肉包子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 你那个戒指好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的耶 好可爱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是玻璃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 谁给你买的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己买戒指说明你很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 不敢相信呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦啊 都染开了 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只能重画了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易画这么好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间了 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好去买新纸了 还有剩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 反正我现在没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要涂色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野好温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学 借一只刷子给矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时净偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这种时候跑出来装相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戏时主角是最累的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他平时确实总偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可记台词还是很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说还是干了该干的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥同学太小看矢野了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人要是说矢野什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是要么岔开话题 要么给予反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被山本同学说时就一句也不回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 那果然是因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吧 她是奈奈的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈 是矢野初中时交往的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是去年在交通事故中去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能接受的 就是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她妹妹又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈的死又不是矢野害的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该被谴责的反而是奈奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但背叛了矢野 还那样就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真该怨恨的不是她妹妹而是矢野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 小水 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太小看矢野了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是很正常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 是山本同学很怪啦 绝对是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是喜欢矢野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也有这个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 她是被甩之后怀恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得山本同学不是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是吧 她不是那么单纯的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不喜欢山本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我觉得她在那方面还是通情理的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我刚才就想要说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么矢野对山本同学那么客气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像对她有愧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没跟山本同学解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小竹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去顺道去下市场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件很想要的长袖T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要几件T恤才够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买多少也不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 病了病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用像刚才那样帮我说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我觉得矢野你很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这种事情不说也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我太多事儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不 起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗那么刁难她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 不很正常嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就应该对她温柔些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就很松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化部推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望之峰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年七班 我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是担任这次班级小剧场监制的小坂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望之峰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁看了都潸然泪下的杰作剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来文化祭就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排练也差不多到了最后关头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 后天就正演了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不练习也没关系了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“快点正演吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应该是这种感觉的最后关头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上是一点这种感觉都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野君 你练习太偷懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快练吧 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着一点儿干劲都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有人说那家伙该做的一定会做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也只有相信了吧 七七
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说了 我不会再说多余的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那么从剧本第25页的戏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手持锄头的人拔刀我心怆然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这对武士来说也甚是可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想说难听的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你放下锄头 乖乖按我说的做就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我就不保 你 性 命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 读得干巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要带着感情啊 感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啥 难道你现在还不会背台词么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个又长又多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天就正演啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正演时有人拿提示版嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该做的完全没做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正演没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 你倒是说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是班长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这跟那个没什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也为了自己的角色尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天啊 后天就正演了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天 你死记也得把台词记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正演的时候一下子就记下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子 一下子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胃痛起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这字怎么念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是kyoku rin zan还是goku rin zan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还在这阶段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视线 错开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用像刚才那样帮我说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去吃肉包子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口借我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂矢野你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能像之前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我从周游全国的僧人那听到了奇妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这极凛山峰顶生着鲜艳的苔藓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采下那种苔藓种在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多贫瘠的土地都会变得丰饶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们将消除隔阂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界将变得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 人们便称极凛山的峰为希望之峰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野有时候真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 好棒 好棒的演技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 想对矢野说“你好厉害啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话 我还有台词的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有三句耶 三句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 你还是那么马虎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 来了这么多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野果然很受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望演出成功啊 七七
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 矢野在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊 正换衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙总是把时间掐得很紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说他少根筋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我演一个村姑才三句台词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的厚脸皮怎么不分给我点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不跟他说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 都是来看你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 今天就拜托你了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始的台词是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 全部忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象你表演成功的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝几口水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧本剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着看这种东西也没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你一定能做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 准备上台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 Let go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又做了多余的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 什么来着 那个山叫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是极凛山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对对 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,峰顶叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望之峰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词都是胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观众们都没有察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是有口才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种舞台气魄 超常发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用帮我说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没错得那么离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪句才是矢野的真心话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士大人 请您先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的一急就摔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆满成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这个好重哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 换手了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 七七
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指上的宝石掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是你自己买的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 很喜欢这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死这种话可不能乱讲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天我真因为车祸之类的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的错可你也不是滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有那么巧的车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来不这么讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和野蛮的高桥不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停停停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之呢 去死这种话不够狠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够狠?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那改说我宰了你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥是流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停停停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能像以前一样跟他说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得死了比较轻松吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把手指一根根伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完后再把指甲一片片…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你是虐待狂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人死之后什么都感觉不到 什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野总是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我觉得近在咫尺却远在天边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说情侣要到前面跳贴面舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野刚刚也被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿手的事情是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野正被告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\fn@simhei\pos(410,110)\fs18\fad(0,250)}黏合剂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 拿错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你修吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你那怪戒指太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴不上 你胖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是戴拇指的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是这根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像结婚典礼上交换戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚典礼的誓词真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意娶她为妻 并发誓永远爱她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我们结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不留神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别笑了 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是发誓还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我就会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把手指伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了 疯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只说一次 你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}远方传来了烟火的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.30,0:25:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.60,0:25:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼中世界的颜色奇迹般地焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.40,0:25:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是矢野施了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.30,0:25:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 矢野 圣诞节礼物你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.60,0:25:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要七七
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.00,0:25:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你认真点儿回答
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.00,0:25:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了 圣诞节的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要答应我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:56.80,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}じゃあまたね　手を振った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:01.90,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}後ろ姿あんなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:09.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕暮れの人波に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:14.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れながら小さくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:23.80,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたがくれた言葉を　ひとつずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:30.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出し 目を閉じた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:43.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せな思いだけ　ここにあるはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:50.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不安になる　どうしてなの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:56.30,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心が震えてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:02.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいもっとそう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:08.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溢れてる　この気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:15.90,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだから　好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:21.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}绝対好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:31.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向いて　駆け出して
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.30,0:24:37.10,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追いかけて行きたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.00,0:24:44.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕暮れの寂しさが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.60,0:24:48.90,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな勇気饮み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.20,0:24:59.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの笑顔の中に　私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.40,0:25:05.10,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少し離れただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.60,0:25:11.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷子になったような
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.00,0:25:18.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}子供みたいに泣き出しそう
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.00,0:25:25.10,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直なら　こんな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:31.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}しなくてもすむのになぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.90,0:25:34.30,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}からっぽのあたしだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:56.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}说声再见 我挥了挥手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:01.90,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的背影如此迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:09.60,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕阳之下 人海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:14.60,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}微微晃动渐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:23.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:30.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一字一句回忆你的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:43.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这里应有的 明明只是幸福的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:50.60,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可是为何心中会有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:56.30,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}原来是我心悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:02.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想告诉你更多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:08.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这满溢的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:15.90,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我喜欢你  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:21.60,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我绝对喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:31.50,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}回过头去 迈出脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.30,0:24:37.10,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想追上前行的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.00,0:24:44.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可傍晚的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.60,0:24:48.90,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}吞没了那份勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.20,0:24:59.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你笑容里 虽有我的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.40,0:25:05.10,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却已然疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.60,0:25:11.60,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我像是迷路的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.00,0:25:18.50,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快要嚎啕大哭
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.00,0:25:25.10,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果坦诚相对
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:31.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就不会这样思念
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.90,0:25:34.30,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有空虚的我
